OL,3,CMan charged after charity coin
OL,4,Ccollector containing #300 stolen
OL,6,FLancashire Police have charged a man
OL,7,Fafter a charity coin collector
OL,8,Fcontaining #300 was stolen from
OL,9,FMcDonalds in Leyland.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to the restaurant
OL,12,Flast Tuesday, 28th April 2026,
OL,13,Ffollowing reports a man had entered,
OL,14,Fpicked up the charity coin collector
OL,15,Fand left the building.
OL,17,FLater in the day, two beer kegs were
OL,18,Fstolen from Go Local on Leyland Lane
OL,19,Fby a man matching the same description.
