OL,3,CMan charged after charity coin
OL,4,Ccollector containing #300 stolen
OL,6,FYesterday, following multiple
OL,7,Fenquiries, a 31 year old man from
OL,8,FLeyland was arrested.
OL,10,FWayne Collins, 31, of Northbrook
OL,11,FGardens, Leyland has been charged with
OL,12,Ftheft from a shop and theft ` other `
OL,13,Fincluding theft by finding.
OL,15,FHe will appear at Preston Magistrates
OL,16,FCourt on 22nd May.
